entries.femaleVariant: But no gonk shit. We don't touch the dancers, we don't go lookin' for a beat-down. All right?
Choom, who you think I am? Look at me. I'm chill. I'm zen. I won't do nothin'.
Yeah, yeah, I know you. Four beers in, you're tryin' to pound some gonk into the pavement.
But this isn't some no-name dive. The Animals huscle here, got it?
First strike, they'll be polite about it, warn ya.
Second strike, you wake up in the gutter with a shattered jaw. Best case scenario.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Pinche" b="" a="... don't be so dramatic."/>
